text: haey nowpel del anak( mou ham meat) bankheunh puokke kampoung b ndouh bangaeab ayeat robsa yeung noh chaur anak ngeak chenhpi puokke tealte puokke chchekaknea pi banhhea phe sa ng vinh . te brasenbae shai t n thveu aoy anak phe lch kraoyomk anak ban nukkheunh vinh noh chaur anak kom angkouy cheamuoy krom del bampean teangnoh aoy saoh
